snippet.title: Doomsday Hunters 1.0
snippet.description:
After what looks like a millenium in the works, our roguelike twin-stick shooter filled with unique features and amazing pixel art looks, will be available on Nintendo Switch as well as Steam on July 20th, 2023!
Preorder on Switch and get -15 discount:
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/doomsday-hunters-switch/
Buy/Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1175360/Doomsday_Hunters/
